1. *Strašna* oluja je uništila polja. (A *terrible* storm destroyed the fields.)
2. Ova knjiga je *strašno* dosadna. (This book is *terribly* boring.)
3. Nisam *strašno* siguran da li je to istina. (I'm not *terribly* sure if that's true.)
4. Ona je *strašno* lepa. (She is *terribly* beautiful.)
5. Sinoć sam imao *strašan* san. (Last night I had a *terrifying* dream.)
6. Ovo je *strašan* problem koji treba rešiti. (This is a *terrible* problem that needs to be solved.)
7. *Strašno* me boli glava. (I have a *terrible* headache.)
8. Film je bio *strašan*. (The movie was *terrifying*.) 
9. Imala je *strašne* oči koje su me plašile. (She had *terrifying* eyes that scared me.)
10. *Strašno* je što smo izgubili utakmicu. (It's *terrible* that we lost the game.)